metadata.name: Christmas Pups #1- Dogs4Ukraine
metadata.description:
A Christmas charity initiative by the Junkyard Dogs to raise money for the dogs of Ukraine. 100% of money raised will go directly to helping street dogs via Big Little Life Rescue charity.

To read more about the work being done in Ukraine, check out our twitter [https://twitter.com/JunkyardDogsNFT](https://twitter.com/JunkyardDogsNFT) and our charity partners at [https://biglittleliferescue.org/](https://biglittleliferescue.org/)
